item.title: Tracking Data for Bar-tailed Godwits (Limosa lapponica)
item.description: Abstract This metadata document describes the data contained in the “rawData” folder of this data package. This data package contains all data collected by the Argos System from 63 satellite transmitters attached to Bar-tailed Godwits on their breeding range in arctic and western Alaska, 2005-2010. Five data files are included in the “rawData” folder of this data package. Two data files (with identical content) contain the raw Argos DIAG (Diagnostic) data, one in the legacy verbose ASCII format and one in a tabular Comma Separate Value (CSV) format.
